    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "I am Utsav writing this letter in regard to my credit card statement which I received yesterday. My credit card number is 4567-5678-1234.",
        "To begin with, the statement exhibits that I have bought two new cellular devices online from Amazon",
        "India on the 18th of September. That being said, I am certainly sure of the fact that I did not use my credit card to make any purchases in the last three (3) months. Furthermore, my credit card expired 3 months ago and I have yet to receive my new plastic card through postal services.",
        "Considering all the above, I would like you to investigate the matter at your earliest convenience and send me an email highlighting the time it will take for you and your team to resolve the matter fully. Moreover, I will be looking forward to your prompt support as always.",
        "Please feel free to call me on my cellular phone in case of any queries.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Utsav Chandel"
